        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         ST will last 18 seconds every time.  any form of damage (incluiding DoTs) will break ST (as it will any mez).</P><P><BR>with ST breaking best thing to do is ST a mob and run the other back...once you have the other back a bit FD.  now at your level you just need to FD and get back up.  when you start killing 34+ mobs you would have to FD and wait for ST to wear off, and then you could get up.  ST has a chance to wipe memory so you don't need to FD, but no reason to take a chance.</P><P><a href="http://www.theinverselogic.com/" target="_blank"><BR>Abillister "Monkey" Abu<BR>Inverse Logic</a><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
