         I used this tactic to break up and solo the MM Graveyard.  It works great.  ST is ocationally resisted, but when it isn't, it always lasts the full duration ( I thought it was 15 sec, but it could be 18).  When splitting 2 mobs, I ST, make sure pet is on second, through one dot (Vamp curse usually), FD till ST wears off.</P><P>Suetekh<BR>Necromancer of 35 Reanimations<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
